description: ASDF--- A collection of animated abstract visuals with different styles and palettes  The initial price for this collection ranges from 1 to 20 tezos and every saturday or sunday the price of the artwork will change until is bought, there will be always a unique piece and there will be no cap amount of price of each one.  The price change will be based in the following formula and it will apply every time saturday or sunday comes: lp=(ap*ap) (at anytime)  lp= latest or initial price  ap= actual price
